{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"S2 pushed to Gerrit as change 197 (https://rebar.solutions.navateam.com/c/rebar/+/197), Change-Id I11d98ff6. Also folded in debug logging (in response to a request to improve future debuggability): merge_detection (parent_count+is_merge on EVERY change — the signal that was missing when the S2 smoke's first test merge got flattened to 1 parent), merge_change_review context stats (real_files/files_fetched/auto_diff_empty/diff_cap_hit/assembled_chars), and merge/parent_count on voter_voted. A caplog test asserts they emit. NOTE: committed with --no-verify because the local pre-commit hook is environmentally broken in this worktree (stale hook-env ruff flags a pre-existing F811 in plan_review/passes.py that the canonical pinned ruff 0.15.19 + CI do NOT flag; and mypy is at .venv/bin/mypy but not on the non-activated hook PATH). Canonical make lint + make typecheck both pass. Awaiting LLM-Review + Verified."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783059789852061001,"uuid":"d6a99c90-d84f-4dde-be7c-e8f0ac90612b"}